description: Prohibition-era Havana cocktail named for the silent-film star — rum, pineapple, grenadine, maraschino.
author: Fred Kaufman (disputed with Eddie Woelke, c. 1922, Havana)
year: c. 1922
venue: Hotel Nacional / Hotel Sevilla, Havana
